{
  "stem": "3804.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] So now, what happened to me is, when I hold him, and I said, how is it-- and that was really it happened to me-- how is it that this guy, like me and you, a man like me and you, did all these atrocities, killing of people, children, women?",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How could it happen that he is the man?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, and if he is the guy, what makes a man to be-- to become Eichmann?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I have to know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And suddenly, it came to me like, you know, a feeling that I have to ask him about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't know exactly how it would be, but this was the turning point in me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said-- the question was, why-- how did you do it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Who is he?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "How did it become that he became Eichmann, such a man that he ordered millions of people, 1 million of children, to go to their death in the concentration camps?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I had to understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And at the time, you were under orders not to speak with him?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Normally, nobody said to you not to speak, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's for granted that you don't speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are a man of a operation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Normally, you don't have to-- I never had a problem to speak, because I never met people, I met documents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't have a problem to speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, the orders are, you don't speak with a spy, or this kind of thing, not a criminal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was something else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I asked myself, why shouldn't I speak with him?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- it was-- nobody told me not to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's normally that, traditionally, you don't speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
